ğŸ¯ Step 4: Define Milestones

Milestones mark major achievements (zero-duration tasks).
Add these below your relevant tasks:

Milestone Name	Linked Task	Duration
Requirements Approved	After Requirements Gathering	0 days
Design Completed	After System Design	0 days
System Live	After Deployment	0 days
Project Closed	After Project Closure	0 days

In ProjectManager, you can mark a task as a milestone by setting its duration to 0 days or checking the Milestone box.

